Sentencas: Direct biomass fuel were tested as fuels for operating micro- solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Direct Biomass Fuel Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: In this study two types of biomass fuels were used viz., Biomethane and rice husk based syngas.
Titulo: Direct Biomass Fuel Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Species present in these fuels were analyzed using gas chromatography.
Titulo: Direct Biomass Fuel Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: It showed that biomethane is composed of N-2 and CH4 whereas syngas comprised of CO2, H-2, N-2, CH4 and CO.
Titulo: Direct Biomass Fuel Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: During the performance study of the fuel cell, it was observed that syngas when used as fuel operated the cell at lower power density than that of biomethane.
Titulo: Direct Biomass Fuel Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Thus an optimal combination of fuel and temperature can serve as a best power source for portable applications.
Titulo: Direct Biomass Fuel Micro-Solid Oxide Fuel Cell
